{"tid":572840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戶口突然多咗48萬，去報案反被威嚇隨時要坐監！","createTime":"2018-02-26T02:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T10:06:13.000Z","uid":1886,"like":74,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"1ffbefe29450420ac0449c2fb354b5cb6403b974","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"「本來在很多人眼中，擁有48萬元是很開心的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但變相我要監察款項不會被扣除一分一毫，很大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」話說Yedda某日提款時發現戶口突然出現一筆來歷不明的48萬存款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，在驚與喜交集下，她最終決定去警署報案自保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，豈料警員的反應卻嚇壞她<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180221/large/1519201893_37df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180221%2Flarge%2F1519201893_37df.jpg&h=055981d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180226/2_572693_0/-橫財害慘我-戶口多近50萬-港女報案反被指隨時坐監\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F2_572693_0%2F-%E6%A9%AB%E8%B2%A1%E5%AE%B3%E6%85%98%E6%88%91-%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%9A%E8%BF%9150%E8%90%AC-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%A3&d=Z54oJ6CSA4JkzC1adIlY6sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9895ce1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F2_572693_0%2F-%E6%A9%AB%E8%B2%A1%E5%AE%B3%E6%85%98%E6%88%91-%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%9A%E8%BF%9150%E8%90%AC-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%A3&h=35ec3ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180226/2_572693_0/-橫財害慘我-戶口多近50萬-港女報案反被指隨時坐監</a></div>"},{"pid":"f9d4b625389b279fcdd675307bb675ee3c565d3b","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":218,"dislike":1,"score":217,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"「由於這是出糧戶口，每月有不少繳費項目要自動轉帳，差人話我如果從48萬款項中被扣除多了一元，我隨時要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！我係良好市民，主動向你報案，但好似千錯萬錯都可能係我一個人錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我好驚同感到好無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」"},{"pid":"aadc30fb3ca95a980a930eeff6fee38b602d8d90","tid":572840,"uid":77196,"like":228,"dislike":1,"score":227,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"死警犬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613161a8f6738f5766e077ea8b2dbeecf63bbf56","tid":572840,"uid":105908,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"依家用幾多 遲啲都嘔突<br />\n好彩揀左報驚"},{"pid":"01b6197bec2ea654275f4eda4f4c8ecf484a6ba9","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":294,"dislike":5,"score":289,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"Yedda過去曾被盗用身份證，最後遭不法之徒在財務公司成功申請借貸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，導致環聯信貨紀錄評級欠佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「我好擔心，以為48萬是係來自財務公司，所以選擇報警，從而了解此筆款項的來歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」 <br />\n<br />\n翌日感到無助之際，親身前往銀行求助，「職員話無法處理，叫我先登記，申請查看支票，好彩支票上有聯絡人電話，款項證實係來自支那的生意人，由於支票無寫枱頭，再錯誤過錯數。」 <br />\n<br />\n事件糾纏王小姐一星期後，入錯數的雙方終相約見面，款項最終順利歸還事主，入錯戶口的李小姐狠批整個過程是要靠雙方自行聯繫，警方和銀行均沒有參與置之不理，十分離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d923526b556cdc9eddaf19c39c1be8870ed8ff59","tid":572840,"uid":38757,"like":2,"dislike":60,"score":-58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"其實同銀行講最直接"},{"pid":"1881ed43530a38b93fd71f81d2379032733a6654","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":94,"dislike":4,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"烏龍苦主王小姐憶述事件，事發當日過錯數後已即時向銀行求助，要求代為聯絡收款人，惟職員的冷漠態度令她深感無奈及沮喪，「職員話無資格代為聯絡，銀行只會發信件，如對方願意配合就會退回款項給我，如不配合先要報警。好彩我今次遇到好心人先攞得番筆錢，如果遇上貪心的人，對方洗晒48萬，我點算，到時候報警都無用。」她指出事件如發生在支那，報案後銀行的處理方法會較為果斷，會先凍結該賬戶，她質疑香港銀行的處理手法「太死板」。"},{"pid":"fa594b2253a995aee60c687ea469075ff3ec0208","tid":572840,"uid":108467,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c64ea0b4386c18c2f399d78ec1021a580e8edc","tid":572840,"uid":63909,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"01b6197bec2ea654275f4eda4f4c8ecf484a6ba9","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":294,"dislike":5,"score":289,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"Yedda過去曾被盗用身份證，最後遭不法之徒在財務公司成功申請借貸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，導致環聯信貨紀錄評級欠佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「我好擔心，以為48萬是係來自財務公司，所以選擇報警，從而了解此筆款項的來歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」 <br />\n<br />\n翌日感到無助之際，親身前往銀行求助，「職員話無法處理，叫我先登記，申請查看支票，好彩支票上有聯絡人電話，款項證實係來自支那的生意人，由於支票無寫枱頭，再錯誤過錯數。」 <br />\n<br />\n事件糾纏王小姐一星期後，入錯數的雙方終相約見面，款項最終順利歸還事主，入錯戶口的李小姐狠批整個過程是要靠雙方自行聯繫，警方和銀行均沒有參與置之不理，十分離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"入錯戶口的李小姐狠批整個過程是要靠雙方自行''聯繫''<br />\n<br />\n聯佢老母繫"},{"pid":"e64a7b78332fb7018d1a6e73490051c9ba9c2d34","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":133,"dislike":4,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180220/large/1519112205_16ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519112205_16ff.jpg&h=8d3567fe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n面對突然飛來橫財， 人生交叉點，Yedda坦言被朋友笑她很傻，不應退回款項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，應盡情花光來享受人生，友人甚至跟她詳談「善用款項」的計劃。「讓我再重新選擇，我都會咁做，我好冷靜考慮，要對得住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，即使你取走48萬去環遊世界，做人卻不會安樂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」"},{"pid":"a87bcd02bf7e38f7b8ca2933f409d0e05e020bd2","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"19c64ea0b4386c18c2f399d78ec1021a580e8edc","tid":572840,"uid":63909,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"01b6197bec2ea654275f4eda4f4c8ecf484a6ba9","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":294,"dislike":5,"score":289,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"Yedda過去曾被盗用身份證，最後遭不法之徒在財務公司成功申請借貸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，導致環聯信貨紀錄評級欠佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「我好擔心，以為48萬是係來自財務公司，所以選擇報警，從而了解此筆款項的來歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」 <br />\n<br />\n翌日感到無助之際，親身前往銀行求助，「職員話無法處理，叫我先登記，申請查看支票，好彩支票上有聯絡人電話，款項證實係來自支那的生意人，由於支票無寫枱頭，再錯誤過錯數。」 <br />\n<br />\n事件糾纏王小姐一星期後，入錯數的雙方終相約見面，款項最終順利歸還事主，入錯戶口的李小姐狠批整個過程是要靠雙方自行聯繫，警方和銀行均沒有參與置之不理，十分離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"入錯戶口的李小姐狠批整個過程是要靠雙方自行''聯繫''<br />\n<br />\n聯佢老母繫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"原文係聯系"},{"pid":"3120d6dcba28bdc6376dac681670de9c638838cc","tid":572840,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a87bcd02bf7e38f7b8ca2933f409d0e05e020bd2","tid":572840,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"19c64ea0b4386c18c2f399d78ec1021a580e8edc","tid":572840,"uid":63909,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"01b6197bec2ea